						               													<description>In Colony X, you play the role of a space foreman working for a billion dollar corporation. Your mission? Establish a sustainable colony on a distant planet.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Colony X is a 2-4 player game featuring area control and colony building. Each turn players land one of their ships on a nearby planet to collect two resources from an ever-changing pool of resources or use one of their ships to visit an architect to construct a new building for their colony. But be warned, after construction future buildings will cost less for your opponents.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game takes place over four rounds. At the end of each round, the player with the most ships on a planet gains its influence token which is needed to complete work orders and increase the value of certain buildings.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At the end of the final round, the player with the most Victory Points tallied from their buildings, influence, and completed work orders is the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
